Name: Darkness Rollercoaster - Ultimate Shooter Edition
About the game: Darkness rollercaster is an Arcade / Shooter where the player has to face enemies in a variety of environments. Dive into Cave, Space, Fantasy land and more to live this amazing railshooter adventure ! Shoot enemies with your game controller (3D Rudder Compatible), block their attacks with your shield or slow down time. But beware of the pitfalls and obstacles you will need to avoid when moving your vehicle at any time! Activate your special vision to recover all the secrets and defeat the final boss ... Compare your score with your friends and win the best shooter trophies! Do you want to live a fantastic experience that will hook you to your seat? Do you like action, emotions and sensations? + This version also include the Soundtrack pack for Anniversary edition. More than 20 musics await you in a level specially designed to listen to them or the decorations light up to the rhythm of the musics. Try Rollercoaster Darkness - The Ultimate Shooter Edition!
